His rework as of 7/17/2020 is pretty damn good so this is kinda obsolete now

Remake: Squall Leonhart (FFVIII)
Weapon type: Sword
Crystal Color: Black
Spheres: A A A

///
Before digging in to this: Squall's battle stance and skill animations are all way cooler in 012. So, that's what I'm basing this off of.
///

Skill 1: Solid Barrel
 4-hit Melee BRV attack.
 If BRV reaches at least 50% Max BRV after the last BRV hit, adds an additional 3-hit Melee BRV attack.
 Uses: 6
15cp: Twin Lance
 +Increases BRV potency
 +Grants ATK Up (40%) and Max BRV Up (40%) to self for 6 turns after initial BRV attack
c.55: Solid Barrel Extend
 +Adds 2 uses
 +Becomes a 4-hit Melee BRV+HP attack
 +If BRV reaches at least 50% Max BRV after the last BRV hit, adds an additional 1-hit Melee BRV+HP attack, triggered 3 times.
 +Increases own BRV by 10% of HP damage dealt after each HP attack (excl. last)

Skill 2: Revolver Drive
 Gain BRV based on own ATK (50%) before a 3-hit Melee BRV+HP attack.
 Grants [Lionheart] to self for 3 turns.
 Uses: 5
35cp: Cutting Trigger
 +Increases BRV potency
 +Increases BRV gain based on ATK (+50%)
 +Extends duration of [Lionheart] by 3 turns
c.60: Rough Divide Extend
 +Adds 2 uses
 +Greatly increases BRV gain based on ATK (+100%)
 +Becomes a 3-hit Melee BRV+HP attack triggered twice
 +Tremendously increases BRV potency
 +Increases own BRV based on 20% of HP damage dealt after first HP attack.
 +Deals 50% TOTAL splash HP damage to non-targets on final HP attack
 
[Lionheart]: ATK Up (50%), INT BRV Up (60%), BRV Regen (80% iBRV)
 
EX: Shear Trigger
 +Equips EX ability Renzokuken
 8-hit Melee BRV+HP attack.
 Allows for 150% Stolen BRV overflow.
 Triggers Rough Divide after use if HP damage dealt equals at least 120% Max BRV.
 Inflicts [Draw] on target for 4 turns.
 Grants [Junction] to self for 4 turns.
Rough Divide:
 3-hit AoE Melee BRV+ST HP attack.
 Deals increased BRV damage when attacking a single target.
 Recast: Slightly Slow
  -LB1: Increases BRV damage dealt by 10%
  -LB2: Extends base duration of [Draw] and [Junction] by 2 turns
  -LB3: Increases recast speed of Renzokuken by 20%
 EX+: Turns BRV Attack to BRV Attack+, HP Attack to HP Attack+
      Renzokuken:
      -Greatly increases BRV potency
      -Extends base duration of [Draw] and [Junction] by 2 turns
      Rough Divide:
      -Tremendously increases BRV potency
      -Allows for 120% Stolen BRV overflow
      -Deals 20% splash HP damage to non-targets
  -LB1: Increases own ATK (50%) and Max BRV (50%)
  -LB2: At Quest start:
        Grants ATK Up (40%) and Max BRV Up (40%) to self for 6 turns
        Grants [Lionheart] to self for 6 turns
  -LB3: Turns BRV Attack, BRV Attack+ to BRV Attack++
        Turns HP Attack, HP Attack+ to HP Attack++
        Renzokuken:
        -Further increases BRV potency
        -Allows for 180% Stolen BRV overflow
        Rough Divide:
        -Becomes a 5-hit AoE Melee BRV+ST HP attack
        -Allows for 150% Stolen BRV overflow
        -Deals 20% splash HP damage to non-targets
        

[Draw]: Will randomly select one of the following effects to apply to target:
        -ATK Down (50%)
        -SPD Down (50%)
        -Max BRV Down (50%)
[Junction]: Grants one of three effects based on the stat debuffed by [Draw]:
            -ATK Up (50%)
            -SPD Up (50%)
            -Max BRV Up (50%)
BRV Attack+: 4-hit Melee BRV attack
BRV Attack++: 4-hit Melee BRV attack
              Last hit is AoE
HP Attack+: 2-hit Melee BRV+HP attack
HP Attack++: 3-hit Melee BRV+HP attack
             Deals 20% splash HP damage to non-targets

LD: Organix
 +Equips LD ability Fated Circle
 3-hit AoE Ranged BRV+HP attack, triggered twice.
 HP damage dealt is split evenly.
 Increases own BRV based on 20% of HP damage dealt after first HP attack.
 Allows for 120% Stolen BRV overflow.
 Grants special effect [Roaring Hammer] to self for 8 turns.
 Uses: 3
  -LB1: Increases own ATK (20%)
        Increases BRV damage dealt by 10%
  -LB2: Increases own ATK (20%)
        Extends duration of [Roaring Hammer] by 8 turns
  -LB3: Increases own ATK (20%)
        Adds 1 use
Board Passive: Fated Circle Extend
 +Becomes a 4-hit AoE Ranged BRV+HP attack, triggered twice
 +Greatly increases BRV potency
 +Allows for 150% Stolen BRV overflow
 +Increases BRV gain based on HP damage dealt (+10%)
 
[Roaring Hammer]: Raises own ATK (50%) and Stolen BRV Overflow Limit (+30%)

BT: Blasting Edge
 +Equips BT ability Blasting Zone
15-HIT AoE melee BRV attack + AoE HP attack
Moderately raises BRV damage dealt when attacking single target
HP damage is split equally amongst all enemies
Maximum BRV damage limit +20%
Maximum HP damage limit +100%

BURST Effect (4 turns, party-wide):
 -Moderately raises HP damage dealt (on non-targets) by abilities with splash damage (+50%)

BT Theme: Force Your Way (VIII)
